profile:
SteriGleam Janitorial Corp. is a commercial cleaning company providing custodian services to office spaces, medical health centres, dental clinics, pharmacies, retail stores, and apartment buildings. While other companies clean, we offer value to our customers by incorporating modern laboratory and medical sterilization and sanitation procedures within our processes.

All of our staff continually trains in the latest compliance methods and are insured and bonded. In addition to our janitorial services, we provide third-party sterilization compliance testing through adenosine triphosphate (ATP) bioluminescence measurements, laboratory pathogen surface analysis, and quality medical and janitorial supplies from national vendors.

We have over 15 years of experience in maintaining intensive care units, operating rooms, emergency departments, and medical analysis clinics.

We Will Make Your Place Virus-Free And Clean
D&N Hygienics caters to the needs of residential and commercial areas alike. We focus on providing various services to our clientele such as sanitizing, disinfecting, cleaning (both manually and mechanically), and sterilizing. Depending on the area and the specific use of the location we provide cross servicing to ensure the highest level of cleanliness and safety.

Here at D&N Hygienics, we look past the cleanliness of our clients residents and businesses. We strive to build personal relationships with each and every one of our clients, new and old. Not only are we concerned with the cleanliness and safety of the environments we work in, but further, we strive to ensure that all our clients have a deep understanding of our services and applications.

We understand that different residents and businesses may have different requirements that must be met, therefore, we focus on adaptability from client to client, home to home, and business to business.

Our company has been consistently recognized by many of our clients as one of the most reliable companies they have come across. We take great pride in that and look forward to maintaining our reputation.

Military Maintenance and Military Maid was founded on the principles of reliability, quality workmanship, and fair pricing. We pride ourselves on helping our customers complete their projects on time and within budget.

The Military Maintenance branch includes carpenters, plumbers, electricians, painters and professional handyman to complete any project you have in mind. We Work Closely with Our team to get best results.

The Military Maid branch of our team handles all the heavy duty cleaning services required at homes and offices. We can clean anything with no job being too big for our team, weve seen it all. 



MILITARY MAID

Our team of dedicated professionals will treat your home like their own. We will always provide our honest and professional opinion to ensure you get the best advice for your home.
Our in-house team of professionals can handle all tasks from large scale renovations to down to the smallest repairs. What does this mean? It means you get the highest quality of work without paying the large markup fees associated when work is subcontracted out. Our hands approach ensures a high level of quality is maintained and pricing is what it should be?
Did you know? Some companies simply outsource the majority of their jobs and markup the pricing anywhere from 25% to 80%! That means you could be drastically overpaying for work by thousands of dollars. Our pricing is based on a simple and fair formula of time and materials. We dont overcharge simply because you own a nice house.
Choose us and know that our dedicated team will take care of you from start to finish and you will be paying a competitive industry price.

Niceview provides fast residential snow removal in all areas of Toronto and GTA. We know your needs are unique, so you can choose from two different levels of service, select all the areas you need cleared, and customize the notes for your booking.

Our team will notify you before your crew arrives and each time the work is completed, with pictures of the freshly cleared paths, sidewalks and driveways. So, if youre at work, out of town, or on vacation  you always know the work has been done!

We look forward to helping you with your snow removal needs this season. All the best to you and yours this winter, take care and be safe!

At Grace Cleaning our service delivery is a key ingredient to our success and the ongoing satisfaction of our clients. To ensure we deliver service excellence every time, we combine close supervision and ongoing training of staff to guarantee each job is completed diligently and comprehensively.

We also maintain regular written inspection reports which are viewed and signed off on by our clients to ensure that at all times they are kept in the communications loop when it comes to their premises.

Our Service. Professional and supervised

Our loyal client base includes long standing relationships which have been developed based on the value and the quality service we offer as well as our ability to continually meet high standards in cleaning and security requirements. We believe it is a combination of our professionalism, commitment to providing the highest quality service and our strong communication with our clients which has resulted in our loyal clientele and our continued business growth.

If you are looking for professional cleaners with years of experience who can get the job done right the first time then you don't need to search any further. Give us a call if youd like to know more.
